data.description:
Welcome to the epitome of Flathead Valley living with this splendid 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house nestled in the heart of our vibrant town. Situated in a prime location, this residence offers the perfect fusion of convenience, comfort, and unique charm.
As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting living space with an open concept, providing a welcoming ambiance for relaxation and entertainment. The well-appointed kitchen boasts new appliances, pantry, and extra storage, making meal preparation a breeze.
Along with new flooring throughout the home, this property includes three bedrooms and a bonus room. The primary bedroom features an en suite bathroom for your convenience. The additional bedrooms & bonus room are versatile, ideal for accommodating guests or transforming into a home office or hobby room.
Outside, the patio area, complete with a pergola and a covered BBQ pit, offers a serene oasis in the midst of the bustling town. It's the perfect spot for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply unwinding after a busy day. And with a great, large gate, it is perfect for storage of campers, boats, and more.
What truly sets this property apart is its unbeatable location. Along with being less than 5 minutes from multiple playgrounds, you'll find yourself within 10 minutes distance to the town's finest dining, shopping, and entertainment options. 
This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours and experience the convenience and vibrancy of Flathead Valley living at its finest. See attached list of Improvements. Video recording on premises. Book a showing today! Call Stephanie Thompson 406-871-8805 or your real estate professional today!
